    {
      "chinese": "當男孩到了青少年時，他們就會到聚會所學習部落的事務。到了十五歲的年齡時，部落的幹部就會帶領他們學習體能訓練、狩獵、堵河水捕魚、敬老尊賢、參加歲時祭儀、學習歌舞等等。由於本身是男性，他們必須學會蓋房子、開山闢土、學習成家立業、以及在部落的聚會所學習長輩所傳襲下來的活動及規範。",
      "ab": "Yo masakapah to ko fa’inayan a wawa i, itini to i sefi ko pinanaman no mira to demak no niyaro’. Tahira moetep ira ko lima ko mihecaan no fa’inayan a wawa i, misakapot to. Keriden no wama no kapah a mikonglin, mi’adop, mitafa’ to nanom a mifoting, mingodo to malitengay, mikihatiya to kiloma’an, minanam to kero ato radiw. O fa’inayan ko tireng, saka o maminanam a misaloma’, mipamatang, miliomah, misaparod, ato minanam to lekakawa no malitengay i sefi no niyaro’.",
      "order": "2",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2022/02/15/7ff95d4aec12150454c3f6e42fc240b9.wav",
